description: Redevelopment of site to provide a 16 storey building (height, scale and bulk of building to remain the same from previous consultation) with new purpose built community facilities for angling club and 100 residential units above comprising 27 x 1 bed, 69 x 2 bed (with a greater number of larger 2-bed/4 person units) and 4 x 3 bed units with associated car parking, cycle parking, refuse storage and amenity space. (Departure from Unitary Development Plan).
